Synopsis
---

Emulate the Linux epoll(7) functions using kqueue(2). 

Usage
---

 Import the epoll.c and epoll.h files into your source tree. Change all instances of

    #include <sys/epoll.h>

 to this:

    #include "epoll.h"

Status
---

  Passes all regression tests under OpenBSD 4.2 and Ubuntu 8.10.

